{"tid":1964184,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實可以再上街抗爭嘅話，必須要以「走住黎屌」嘅模式進行","createTime":"2020-04-08T15:33:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:49:37.000Z","uid":52429,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"886f44e9f058778a54200cc6236f831cf4634b4b","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"就算可以再上街抗爭都係咁話<br />\n因為抗爭者同黑警武力唔對等<br />\n「走住黎屌」呢招同「以空間換取時間」嘅模式差唔多<br />\n又或者咁樣解釋啦, 抗爭者係充當「沙包」咁嘅角色<br />\n一邊走一邊任由黑警追打, 是謂「走住黎屌」<br />\n志在係要拖到英美兩國軍事全面介入香港先有得贏<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/232516_10fff7a70f83447294c671bc920cc976.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F232516_10fff7a70f83447294c671bc920cc976.jpg&h=154b2172&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2a7ddec3feff8608a4e2898809bde842492336b","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68084faaca050eed4cdbc18da06430ff8c2b216b","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b9225f62155dd8dd773f3e8ad9d4c40ebcab4c","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b096fa625a772e90619d3d0681cbeb734470b4","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3160e8c240ad5def7585e0e625bb9dfceae37cc1","tid":1964184,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":